      <section class="section section--muted">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-heading">
            <p class="eyebrow">Our services</p>
            <h2>Services tailored to your drain and sewer needs</h2>
            <p>We do not offer one-size-fits-all solutions. Every service we provide is designed to resolve specific problems quickly and reliably.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="trust-stack">
            <article><span>01</span><div><h3><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/">Drain cleaning services</a></h3><p>Clogged drains do not just slow down your day; they can cause significant damage if left untreated. Our advanced drain cleaning solutions, including mechanical and hydro jetting technologies, clear blockages and restore flow without delay. Whether it is a bathroom sink or a mainline issue, our <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/">drain cleaning service</a> is ready to act.</p><p><strong>Drain cleaning is commonly used to address the following:</strong></p><ul class="check-list"><li>Kitchen and <a href="../common-clogs/">bathroom sinks</a></li><li>Shower and tub drains</li><li>Floor drains</li><li>Main sewer lines</li><li><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/">Outdoor drains</a></li></ul></div></article>
            <article><span>02</span><div><h3><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-cleaning/">Sewer service and cleaning</a></h3><p>A clogged or damaged sewer line can escalate into a full-blown nightmare. We offer professional sewer service to maintain the health of your system. From specialized tools to thorough inspections, our <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-cleaning/">sewer cleaning service</a> ensures blockages and buildup are resolved completely.</p><p><strong>You should call for sewer service when:</strong></p><ul class="check-list"><li>Repeated backups in your toilet or drains</li><li>Unpleasant odors near your property</li><li>Slow draining in multiple fixtures</li><li>Gurgling sounds in pipes</li><li>Unexplained yard changes like soggy patches, sinkholes, or sudden plant overgrowth</li></ul></div></article>
            <article><span>03</span><div><h3><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-and-sewer-inspection/">Video inspections for clarity</a></h3><p>Unsure of what is causing the problem? Our high-definition <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-and-sewer-inspection/">sewer and drain camera inspections</a> look inside your pipes. Using advanced technology, our technicians accurately identify root intrusion, cracks, or severe clogs, paving the way for targeted repairs.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>04</span><div><h3>Rooter service by the experts</h3><p>Tree roots are a common cause of sewer issues, requiring specialized tools and expertise to remove. Our rooter service targets roots and other stubborn blockages while preserving the integrity of your pipes. Honest Drain is equipped to deliver when you need immediate rooter solutions. Whether roots have infiltrated a clay sewer or a cracked fitting, our <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/root-intrusion-repair/">root intrusion repair</a> team handles it quickly and effectively.</p></div></article>
            <article><span>05</span><div><h3><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-repairs/">Drain repairs and upgrades</a></h3><p>Drain damage, from cracked pipes to corroded systems, can lead to water leaks and costly issues. Our skilled technicians repair broken or aging lines with precision, ensuring a reliable drainage system.</p><p><strong>Key <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-repairs/">drain repairs</a> we can complete include:</strong></p><ul class="check-list"><li>Repairing leaks</li><li>Replacing damaged pipe segments</li><li>Upgrading outdated materials</li></ul></div></article>
            <article><span>06</span><div><h3><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/emergency-drain-cleaning/">Emergency services at the speed you need</a></h3><p>Experiencing an emergency? Honest Drain is prepared to respond at a moment's notice. Whether it is a burst sewer line or an overflowing drain, we bring the tools, parts, and expertise to address the problem on the spot. Our <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/emergency-drain-cleaning/">emergency drain cleaning</a> and <a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/emergency-sewer-repair/">emergency sewer repair</a> teams are available 24/7.</p></div></article>
