      <section class="section section--cards section--muted">
        <div class="container section-heading section-heading--left">
          <p class="eyebrow">Residential service categories</p>
          <h2>Drain and sewer services at a glance</h2>
          <p>Each service below has its own page with detailed scope, signs to watch for, and the honest steps Honest Drain takes on the visit.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
          <div class="commercial-service-board"><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-drain-cleaning"><h3 id="group-drain-cleaning"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/">Drain Cleaning</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>01</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/emergency-drain-cleaning/">Emergency Drain Cleaning</a></h4><p>Clogs and blockages can happen anytime. Our team responds quickly with fully equipped service trucks to provide effective solutions and keep your drains flowing smoothly, day or night.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>02</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/basement-drain-cleaning/">Basement Drain Cleaning</a></h4><p>Basement floor drains are the last line of defense before water reaches finished floors. We clear them using advanced jetting and snaking, test them, and explain how to keep them flowing.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>03</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-cleaning/pipe-descaling/">Pipe Descaling</a></h4><p>Cast iron drains in older homes choke on rust, mineral scale, and tubercles. Mechanical descaling restores the inside diameter and preps the line for pipe lining without ripping out the pipe.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-sewer-repair-and-replacement"><h3 id="group-sewer-repair-and-replacement"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/">Sewer Repair and Replacement</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>04</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/emergency-sewer-repair/">Emergency Sewer Repair</a></h4><p>A collapsed or separated sewer cannot be cleaned around. When sewage is surfacing or the line is unusable, emergency sewer repair restores service with flat-rate pricing and no hidden fees.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>05</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/root-intrusion-repair/">Root Intrusion Repair</a></h4><p>Tree roots penetrate sewer lines through small cracks, trapping debris and obstructing wastewater flow. Our rooter service targets roots with hydro jetting, mechanical augers, and professional root treatments.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>06</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-repair-and-replacement/sewer-backup-repair/">Sewer Backup Repair</a></h4><p>A sewer backup is the symptom of a damaged or restricted line. We diagnose with video inspection, clear the blockage, and repair the underlying defect so backups do not return.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-exterior-drain-services"><h3 id="group-exterior-drain-services"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/">Exterior Drain Services</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>07</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/driveway-drain-cleaning/">Driveway Drain Cleaning</a></h4><p>Trench drains, channel drains, and grated inlets across driveways and patios redirect surface runoff. Keep them clear with professional cleaning and the water keeps moving.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>08</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/exterior-drain-services/landscape-drain-services/">Landscape Drain Services</a></h4><p>French drains, catch basins, pop-up emitters, and yard area drains all share the same job: move water away from the house. We clean and maintain them to prevent pooling, erosion, and foundation damage.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-septic-services"><h3 id="group-septic-services"><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/septic-services/">Septic Line Cleaning</a></h3><article class="service-line"><span>09</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/septic-services/">Power Snaking & Hydrojetting Septic Lines</a></h4><p>Septic lines clog with grease, roots, and buildup just like any other drain. Power snaking and hydrojetting clear blockages and restore full flow to inlet, outlet, and distribution lines.</p></div></article></section><section class="service-group" aria-labelledby="group-other"><h3 id="group-other">Other services</h3><article class="service-line"><span>10</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/hydro-jetting/">Hydro Jetting</a></h4><p>High-pressure water at up to 4,000 PSI forcefully removes grease, scale, roots, and debris from the entire pipe wall. When cabling only opens a temporary path, hydro jetting provides a thorough, lasting clean.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>11</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-and-sewer-inspection/">Drain and Sewer Inspection</a></h4><p>High-definition cameras look inside your pipes to identify root intrusion, cracks, leaks, and structural damage without invasive digging. The repair plan is based on evidence, not guesswork.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>12</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-repairs/">Drain Repairs</a></h4><p>Drain damage from cracked pipes to corroded systems can lead to water leaks and costly issues. Our skilled technicians repair broken fittings, replace failing sections, and correct undersized lines.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>13</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/drain-sewer-maintenance/">Drain & Sewer Maintenance</a></h4><p>Most backups are predictable. Customizable maintenance plans with regular inspections, drain cleaning, and sewer cleaning keep the small problems from becoming the big ones.</p></div></article><article class="service-line"><span>14</span><div><h4><a href="../drain-and-sewer-services/sewer-cleaning/">Sewer Cleaning</a></h4><p>A clogged or neglected sewer line can escalate into hazardous backups, property damage, and health risks. Professional sewer cleaning removes grease, soap scum, hair, and invasive tree roots to maintain flow.</p></div></article></section></div>
        </div>
